[quote=&quot;Carrot&quot;:10yobptv]On the [b:10yobptv][Object][/b:10yobptv] tab, add the commands Switch on and Switch of to the [b:10yobptv]Inventory verbs:[/b:10yobptv] pane.

Failing that, can you post your game file.[/quote:10yobptv]

They're already on there.

[code:10yobptv]&lt;!--Saved by Quest 5&#46;4&#46;4873&#46;16527--&gt;
